                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable K</hi> 209.) I took the prisoner and asked what he had done with the money—he said he had received it and lost it in a <hi rend="italic">buss</hi>, and he would pay Mr. Eltham as soon as he could.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I lost the money on the Saturday.</p>
